com.iota.iri.conf

Interface TipSelConfig

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Config
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IotaConfig
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseIotaConfig, MainnetConfig, TestnetConfig

    public interface TipSelConfig
extends Config
    Configuration for how we perform tip selections. Tip selection is invoked when a client wants to find tips to attach its transactions to. The tips are invoked via random walks that start at a certain point in the tangle. The parameters here affect the length and randomness of this walk.
